        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “Atal Kisan Jyoti Yojana” launched by the Energy Department, Government of Madhya Pradesh, aims to provide concessional electricity to farmers through a flat rate power supply of ₹750/- per horsepower per year to metered agricultural pump consumers up to 10 horsepower.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "Electricity Supply at Concessional Rate: Farmers having metered permanent agricultural pumps up to 10 horsepower are provided electricity at a flat rate of ₹750/- per horsepower per year.\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to provide affordable electricity to farmers in Madhya Pradesh by offering power supply at concessional rates.",
